div.p: This integrated map tracks the query lifecycle from raw ASCII to NAND sectors.

ol.li: The Gateway holds heap-allocated buffers for raw strings.
The Compiler performs token analysis and heuristic cost-based planning.
The Engine acts as a virtualized RISC CPU for data processing.
The Backend maps logical rows to physical B-Tree cells and Pager slots.
The Protector ensures that fsync barriers are respected via the WAL.
